Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留意到她也乘同一輛電車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第二學期開學時的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首班前往學園前的列車馬上要發車了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關門請注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道她是鄰班的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很喜歡看書  經常在往返的電車上看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這只是每天乘同一輛電車時的一點點小小的發現而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始在意起她的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但別說詳細地四處調查了  連招呼都沒打過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅是能在遠處注視著她  桂言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.65,0:01:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得  那一整天過得充實多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎  手機的戀愛魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把喜歡的人的照片當作待機圖片保持3個星期
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有讓任何人發現的話  戀愛就能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有讓任何人發現的話  戀愛就能成功嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.96,0:02:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  就是那個戀愛的魔法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤對流行還真敏感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的  而且跟西園寺沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然之間幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起是同桌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照了  伊藤誠同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤好像學習很好的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我說伊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡四班的桂同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  西園寺  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事絕對不要跟別人說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}這就是那個魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.39,0:03:59.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:02.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}那為什麼會有她的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}碰巧拍到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}這種理由誰會信啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.38,0:04:10.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}是啊  我也不信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}她是四班的桂同學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}你別管了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}不用隱瞞哦  她很可愛的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}魔法進行到第幾天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰介
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要偷懶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本都弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和西園寺關係有那麼好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她跟我搭話的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西園寺別看那樣可是很受歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為她只是個煩人的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對女孩的審美觀真是差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  西園寺真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  你喜歡她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的女孩我都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明誠心追求  誠  你也太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我可什麼都沒做  和西園寺之間什麼事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這麼說也只是現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你馬上會扔下我們  跨過成人的那道坎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對方是西園寺  就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自大  又是你贏  只有我的春天永遠不會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你殺了後我也去死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這可不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你絕對是誤解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有別的人在的話  伊藤可能會覺得尷尬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼西園寺有屋頂的鑰匙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是天文部的部長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個一年級學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被廢部好多年了  我自稱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說想觀測天體  很容易就批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上一次都沒做過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不覺得有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個秘密的地方  不覺得刺激  快樂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我現在滿是不安  不覺得快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你叫我過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  伊藤真是急性子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我宣佈了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才和桂同學成為朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育課不是和四班合上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時  怎麼搞到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感興趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學身體很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也是在旁聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也裝病  就和她一起休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝病是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心伊藤嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟偷看到了你的手機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後聊了很多  桂同學的情況好像都瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為桂同學很可愛  在班上很受歡迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  基本沒什麼朋友  很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還拿到了郵件地址和電話號碼  厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算今晚就給她打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體內容之後我也會告訴伊藤的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  西園寺  為什麼要為我做到這個地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤在女孩中可是很受歡迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  果然沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果伊藤有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作為女生代表可不能裝看不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  伊藤生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要戲弄你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰  跟誰說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤好嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  再不會對誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「再」  什麼叫「再」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟誰都沒說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了就讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這讓別人看見了可不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  因為剛才大吃一驚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  伊藤是很老實的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來為你加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是開玩笑  我會好好幫你一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓伊藤的單戀能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給我世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說同意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不交給我的話就說出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  西園寺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫世界就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西園寺世界  世界是「WORLD」的世界哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規模龐大的名字吧  我很喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  很帥氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得我好遜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才對你大聲嚷嚷  真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦  請多多關照  誠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我也直呼其名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那  在等我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟伊藤聊了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那個了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啊  伊藤很有趣  就和他做朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜品店有糯米團拼盤的新品了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  就決定去那了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  誠  現在正在進行中嗎  還是剛開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}對她進行了些調查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}興趣是讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}這我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}每天午飯在學生食堂\N喜歡的食物是雞肉拉麵\N偶爾吃意式實心面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:12.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}愛吃麵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}胸部非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:15.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}在這裏重大宣佈！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}說好了今天和桂同學3個人\N一起吃午飯\N請·多·關·照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:25.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}說好了今天和桂同學3個人一起吃午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不行  絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天到了今天怎麼變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上煲電話時說到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是叫你吃午飯  要理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要  我還沒作好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想像腳就在抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是男子漢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不當男子漢也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就成為男子漢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  說起來  我沒做物理的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個別去管它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問了桂同學喜歡的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道的話就過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學  現在沒有在交往的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有在意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有到喜歡地步的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}有在意的人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要認輸  所以說  誠努力的話還是有機會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是嗎  我知道這個就已經很滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛慕如果只是憑想像是不會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  桂同學  讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西園寺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  久等了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我也是剛剛來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  初次見面  我是桂言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.74,0:13:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我是伊藤誠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在相親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別畏畏縮縮的了  來吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.66,0:13:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  桂同學  這看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不是很拿手  請品嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害  自己做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  特意邀請我來  想總歸要做些什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼費心的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  誠  桂同學親手做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學也是  可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  樂意之極  我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也不錯吧…  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺激舌頭的沒嘗過的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學  難道你做菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  基本上是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是第一次嘗到的味道  舌頭吃了一驚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃  很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好吃到爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像接受了  結局很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就給你倒熱茶  不用太急哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備得真充分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  伊藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣塞過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你這麼沒輕重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一不小心…  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到哪裏去？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我去下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就要祈禱一切順利了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學真是有趣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道原以為我是個可怕的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為你是很冷靜的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時是很冷靜的喲  只是今天比較特別
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  特別是指因為要和桂同學一起吃午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是說只有我們兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上世界是三個人一起  並沒有別的意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  世界去洗手間還真久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  就是說桂同學以前就知道我的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是覺得從西園寺同學那裏瞭解到的和實際感覺不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是呢  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但桂同學果然很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.71,0:16:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常感謝世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  能和桂同學這樣聊天真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只能算是普通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠太晚熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啦  都一個班嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我覺得要是簡單就成了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就沒什麼樂趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若不是世界幫忙的話是絕對不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.66,0:16:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  我打算明天向桂同學表白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許會被甩  但我想好好傳達我現在的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有男人氣概哦  誠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:16:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠的話一定能成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到學園前方向的電車即將進站了  請退到待車線後等待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.21,0:17:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學也乘這輛電車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備  起跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西園寺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身體也不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  西園寺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊藤同學向我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛認識就告白  真是冒失的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得我以前說過有個在意的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得  記得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和誠約會的時候想起那個人可不行喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠很感情很細膩的  知道了一定會難過的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在意的那個人…就是伊藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺每天在電車裏一直有人看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也告訴自己只是自作多情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一在意起來就越來越在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就是伊藤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是兩情相願嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  今天早上被伊藤同學告白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很感謝西園寺同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是西園寺同學介紹讓我們認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是這樣的話  是絕對沒機會和伊藤同學認識的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛慕如果只是憑想像的話  是不會實現的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.16,0:19:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的話我也告訴過誠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那傢伙也說過  只是遠遠看著桂同學就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠其實是很善良的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜歡桂同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒在學校告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.23,0:19:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  在學校大家都在很難說出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等桂同學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂同學說有委員會要開所以要晚點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別心急了做出什麼越軌的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.69,0:20:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電燈泡我可不需要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  我也是坐這條線的班車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  我從沒在車上看見過你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誠是相反路線的車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家在橫手的原阪町喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不是告訴過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼幫我這麼多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偷看了我的電話的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般是不會做到這地步的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為還有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比看別人的戀愛更有趣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視的演藝圈新聞和電視劇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上都是戀愛故事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣二人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是說我的名字而是指這個「WORLD」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣以自己的意志來控制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像明白了…又好像不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這點很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像欠了你一個大人情的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很大喲  花一輩子的時間都償還不完的大喲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}馬上開往原阪町方向的列車就要進站了  請退到黃線以後等候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一定會還這個情的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  不用逞強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算逞強也一定會還
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要做點什麼來回報我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼我都會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  電車也來了  什麼時候都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.33,0:21:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:27.42,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;8;0,{\frz-90}君のことを想う　そのたび
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:33.20,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}上手く息が出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:39.84,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}本当の自分を隠して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:45.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}何が欲しいんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:53.09,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}一番の理解者なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:57.65,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}笑顔見せるかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:24:05.20,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}一つまた嘘がこぼれた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:12.03,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}君が好きなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:15.93,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}この声が枯れるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.15,0:24:21.26,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;8;0,{\frz-90}言葉にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:23.26,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}気付いて…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:34.21,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;15;0,{\frz-90}狭い空の下で　私は君を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:27.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}每當想起你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.87,0:23:33.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}我就會呼吸急促
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:39.84,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;8;0,{\frz-90}一直壓抑著自己深處的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.86,0:23:45.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}我究竟在期盼著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:53.09,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}是想要那個最理解我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:57.65,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}對我綻放笑容吧{\fnMS Gothic}…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:24:05.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;10;0,{\frz-90}我為什麼會再次言不由衷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:12.03,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;12;0,{\frz-90}明明是這樣地愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:15.93,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;11;0,{\frz-90}這樣的心聲要對你重複
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.15,0:24:21.26,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;8;0,{\frz-90}直到聲音嘶啞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.08,0:24:23.26,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;9;0,{\frz-90}留意到了嗎{\fnMS Gothic}…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:34.21,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Scroll up;0;396;15;0,{\frz-90}在這片小小的天空下　我在守望著你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:53.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}預告
